      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about the \"pain\" anymore, it's just the exhaustion. i'm just so tired of pretending it gets better. like, if the person you loved most is gone and the world is still just spinning like nothing happened, what's the point of trying to fix it? it feels like there's no actual way to fix this emptiness.",
